Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就像是迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意不要掉隊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.21,0:01:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是炸藥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這完全潮掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會爆炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 別磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追兵馬上就會追來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴風雪過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.11,0:02:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始準備
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 長官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利及其中央派來的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合計三人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看準空隙做掉他們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 長官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.95,0:02:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由這裡的成員執行作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對北方司令部的人也要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…邁爾斯少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做掉是指殺死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不贊成殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封印他的鍊金術 叫他說出情報比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得那傢伙會說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他活著太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 那傢伙的部下呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人也許只是被迫變成合成獸而聽命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但畢竟只是「也許」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.73,0:03:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只因為可疑就殺死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷文中將那件事 也許還有別的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別忘了布里克斯的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放鬆警惕就會被幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的天真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許哪天會奪去你與同伴的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這地方不需要不謹慎的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利及另兩名 就由我做掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說也是孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 在這個世界要貫穿不殺的理念太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我曾經也有那種想法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了這個年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經歷了幾場戰鬥後就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起殺掉 不殺才更難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛力克兄弟選擇了困難的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好事的傢伙們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 但是也有點羡慕他們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個LaSaYaNa是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠獲得長壽的靈藥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是指賢者之石呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將所有的金屬轉變為金
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將老人變成青年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個AUReRiAN是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金子的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘是有關長生不老與黃金的話題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡先生的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是受了清國鍊丹術的影響呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在清國稱不死之人為 真正的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既「真人」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是完全之人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從金也是完全的金屬這層意思上講
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有把真人稱為金人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全的人是金人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一種說法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把鍊金術傳到清國的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是擁有金髮和金瞳的長生不老之人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才這麼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金髮和金瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是愛德和阿爾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 來這邊 是出口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:05:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全穿越山脈了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在向布里克斯進發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 你們跟著我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來雪很深呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘 坐我背上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走在前面把雪踩實開出一條路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們跟在後面就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.53,0:06:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾馮斯大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾 不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踩到深處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這麼被埋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼阿爾會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿過山脈 先繞過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿過山脈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那暴風雪之中？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有迂迴 筆直過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼做出這麼亂來的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有緊急聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緊急聯絡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央軍進入了布里克斯要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姆斯壯少將也被召去中央了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.78,0:07:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在去要塞很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有藏到別的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說別的地方 我們能去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距離這裡不遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個叫阿斯別克的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說同胞們住在那村子的貧民窟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊修瓦爾的貧民窟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎沒有別的選擇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:07:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾突然不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會被金普利懷疑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊 不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥會隨機應變的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三班 三名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四班 五名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼各自開始搜索所擔當的地區
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 長官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 喂 阿爾馮斯君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才應該說「好的」才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太好走動 愛德華君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 金普利在看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 金普利他們去搜查哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在城鎮中央有個很大的豎坑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要進那裡來調查礦道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為不信任北方的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以只和中央都市派來的部下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙 察覺到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繞到前面去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在豎坑的附近找好狙擊地點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找礦道的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有多個腳印就沒錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 這個距離的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛德華君…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要調查礦道的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給布里克斯兵不是更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面似乎非常複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你特意過來阻止我 也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜對了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想快點把斯卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說在爭取配置狙擊手的時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你注意到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周圍有這麼多殺氣 當然會察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是白白活過了伊修瓦爾戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎在談論什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能只瞄準金普利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開槍 要慎重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 長官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙 用雪做掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這兩個大叔也是合成獸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 什麼都看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 對方也看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半斤對八兩…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖待著 鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在視野不好的地區
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你無法從我們的鼻子下逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鋼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邁爾斯少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有合成獸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我習慣在視野不好的地方戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要進入雪煙裡面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 這樣個子會變矮的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸藥？不愧是礦山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別靠近哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們知道這是什麼吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 那種潮了的東西無法用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔們 知道炸藥的原料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硝化甘油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硝化甘醇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木屑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有硝酸銨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 那個硝酸氨是什麼組成的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是硝酸和氨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氨？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼味道？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是氨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼻子太靈也很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們已經沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心人質 馬上就這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想讓你把知道的事情全都說出來罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 血氣方剛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷剛好就和年輕人戰鬥 看來會費點力氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我也沒空陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓我用這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己拿出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有賢者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鍊成陣也無法用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:14:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.28,0:15:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勝了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這麼想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不殺的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很偉大的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 在戰場上會變成空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那一瞬 你把我殺了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那份天真就是你的敗因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉進豎坑了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真過份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連我們也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 金普利那傢伙去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾？怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾馮斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又被牽走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:17:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被什麼牽走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎麼了 鎧甲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.47,0:17:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾 阿爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靈魂被牽走…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐 以前有過這種事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾馮斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾 阿爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾 阿爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.87,0:17:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能這樣 讓她哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 金普利那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 鋼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼救了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒有幫我把插在肚子上東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔掉的傢伙… 會很困擾…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.22,0:18:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們把那根鋼筋拔出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可是敵人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒有接到殺你的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 拔掉鋼筋的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你立刻就會因大量失血而死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔掉的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大出血之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用鍊金術…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封住傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會用醫療系的鍊金術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要人體鍊成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概研究過了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣子估計內臟完全亂七八糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不像金普利那樣使用賢者之石的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為賢者之石的替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然壽命也許會減少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是猶豫的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是自己的天真導致的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要自己補上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你沒有猶豫的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要拔了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:19:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把自己的生命想像成一種能量體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和賢者之石一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 我現在是份量為靈魂的賢者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.06,0:20:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個使用生命的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擅自把我殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有完全治好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把沒事的組織連接起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時止血的急救措施
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.68,0:21:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 必須得去看醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒有那個閒工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去追金普利才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家很…危…險
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.44,0:21:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 他是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.03,0:21:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種狀態去戰鬥也沒勝算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賢者之石嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是金普利先生拿著的那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要叫他 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.40,0:21:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我們也捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:21:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 和那傢伙說再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們算在這裡死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 這傢伙怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總不能讓他死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.77,0:22:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我們的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.22,0:22:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.41,0:22:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了外面要先去找醫生才行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:23:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斬斷膠著的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.56,0:24:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開創道路所需要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.95,0:24:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外的想法和行動力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現了隱藏之真實的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.42,0:24:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠抓住通向勝利的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.68,0:24:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那需要每天的積累
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.93,0:24:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.45,0:24:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.06,0:24:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第42話 反擊的徵兆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.35,0:24:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 戰爭即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:23.48,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}無止境的旅途中  止步不前之時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:29.75,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}我們深深地歎氣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.81,0:00:37.44,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}再次放開了緊握的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:44.84,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}但是現在已經沒有什麼可怕的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.45,0:00:52.80,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}連接心靈之間那堅固的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:58.23,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}決不會被斬斷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:07.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}繼續尋求 終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.99,0:01:13.75,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}在這個地方畫上句號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.93,0:01:23.07,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}悲傷與憤怒 化為力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.07,0:01:28.03,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}命運就在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.27,0:22:45.24,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本是沒有交點的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.24,0:22:45.99,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今天也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:50.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}企圖奪走我們的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.48,0:22:56.43,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即使獲得了想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:22:57.43,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼卻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.43,0:23:02.41,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}無法坦率地會心一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.09,0:23:08.17,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}流出的眼淚    不代表弱小或後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.79,0:23:12.93,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}只是孕育痛苦的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.59,0:23:17.97,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不論什麼樣的瞬間與命運
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.97,0:23:26.69,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}終於明白了唯一可以確定的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.69,0:23:29.27,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}極限也好  困難也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.27,0:23:33.29,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都不願意放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.29,0:23:38.15,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就這樣決不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.15,0:23:45.98,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}緊握你的右手傳來的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:49.65,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,750)\blur2}就在這裡
